schemas.identityVersionRespXML:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<xsd:schema xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns="http://docs.openstack.org/identity/api/v3">
  <xsd:element name="version">
    <xsd:complexType>
      <xsd:sequence>
        <xsd:element name="media-types" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">
          <xsd:complexType>
            <xsd:sequence>
              <xsd:element name="media-type" maxOccurs="unbounded">
                <xsd:complexType>
                  <xsd:simpleContent>
                    <xsd:extension base="xsd:string">
                      <xsd:attribute name="base" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
                      <xsd:attribute name="type" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
                    </xsd:extension>
                  </xsd:simpleContent>
                </xsd:complexType>
              </xsd:element>
            </xsd:sequence>
          </xsd:complexType>
        </xsd:element>
        <xsd:element name="links" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">
          <xsd:complexType>
            <xsd:sequence>
              <xsd:element name="link" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">
                <xsd:complexType>
                  <xsd:simpleContent>
                    <xsd:extension base="xsd:string">
                      <xsd:attribute name="href" type="xsd:anyURI" use="required"/>
                      <xsd:attribute name="rel" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
                    </xsd:extension>
                  </xsd:simpleContent>
                </xsd:complexType>
              </xsd:element>
            </xsd:sequence>
          </xsd:complexType>
        </xsd:element>
      </xsd:sequence>
      <xsd:attribute name="status" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
      <xsd:attribute name="updated" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
      <xsd:attribute name="id" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
    </xsd:complexType>
    <xsd:attribute name="status" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
    <xsd:attribute name="updated" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
    <xsd:attribute name="id" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
  </xsd:element>
</xsd:schema>

                      </xsd:complexType>
                    </xsd:element>
                  </xsd:sequence>
                </xsd:complexType>
              </xsd:element>
              <xsd:element name="links" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">
                <xsd:complexType>
                  <xsd:sequence>
                    <xsd:element name="link" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1">
                      <xsd:complexType>
                        <xsd:simpleContent>
                          <xsd:extension base="xsd:string">
                            <xsd:attribute name="href" type="xsd:anyURI" use="required"/>
                            <xsd:attribute name="rel" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>
                          </xsd:extension>
                        </xsd:simpleContent>
                      </xsd:complexType>
                    </xsd:element>
                  </xsd:sequence>
                </xsd:complexType>
              </xsd:element>

            <xsd:attribute name="status" type="xsd:normalizedString" use="required"/>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<versions xmlns="http://docs.openstack.org/identity/api/v2.0">
